quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  68,34,righteous ind their Lord gxarden bliss
  68,35,Ni trakt Submitters criminals
  68,36,Ki est wrong kun your logik
  68,37,Vi Do another libr uphold
  68,38,En gxi vi trov anything vi want
  68,39,Vi ricev solen assurances el us ke grant vi whatever vi wish Tag Resurrection
  68,40,Pet them Who garanti this por vi
  68,41,Ili hav idols? Let their idols help them ili est truthful
  68,42,Tag ven when ili exposed ili est required fal prostrate ili est unable al
  68,43,Kun their okul subdued humiliation kovr them. Ili invit fal prostrate when ili est whole able
  68,44,Do let Me deal kun those reject this Hadith; ni plumb them sur whence ili neniam perceive
  68,45,Mi don them suficx sxnur; mi scheming est formidable
  68,46,Vi pet them mon ili sxargx fine
  68,47,Ili kon future Ili Do gxi recorded
  68,48,Vi steadfastly persevere port ordon your Lord Ne est (Jonah) vok fisx
  68,49,Se ne est his Lord's grace li ejected dezert sinner
  68,50,his Lord ben him far him righteous
  68,51,Those disbelieved montr their ridicule their okul when ili auxd message dir Li est crazy
  68,52,Gxi est en fakt message mond